The First Lady of Nigeria, Mrs. Aisha Muhammadu Buhari has congratulated Aisha Dahiru Binani over her victory at the just-concluded governorship primaries of the All Progressives Congress in Adamawa State. The First Lady, in a statement by her Special Assistant on Media & Publicity, Aliyu Abdullahi, described her emergence as the governorship candidate of the APC in Adamawa State as a victory for all Nigerian women. She called on Binani not to rest on her oars, as the journey had just begun. 